    "We used the following hyperparameters to train the CNN-RNN model.",
    "The W-CNN and S-CNN models both have four convolutional layers with detailed structure provided in Table S2 in the Supplementary Material.",
    "In the CNN models, downsampling was performed by average pooling with stride of 2.",
    "The output of W-CNN is followed by a fully connected layer, which has 60 neurons for corn yield prediction and 40 neurons for soybean yield prediction.",
    "The output of the S-CNN model is followed by a fully connected layer that has 40 neurons."
